Didn't have my first class. So I got to sleep in which is good, yes. I got up at noone to get ready to leave at 12:30 for my math class. Had a test due in the class and a test to take in it too. I think I did fairly well. 

Not really much else to report. I watched my John Wayne Gacy dvd. I'm gonna talk about it with Rick on Tuesday. Maybe he can show me the serial killer book thats in the library. I tried to find it but couldn't. 

James, a close friend online, has been feeling down and angry at his parents alot lately. He's a really nice guy and is fun to talk to so I feel bad. He won't talk to me cause he doesn't want to take his anger out on me but I miss our convos. I remember the first one we had over web cam.

James: See? You are black!
Me: Um...James..I'm the palest of the whites here dude. 
James: ....Oh...Yay! 

Got my period too so we know how fun that is. Been craving alot of salt and chocolate. I hate that. I hate what my hormones do to me. So I'm getting on birth control maybe winter break. I dunno. Might wait until summer break. I also want pants. Like really baggy pants. Like what the chick Nancy on E-Bay makes. *wiggleS* Dammit! I wish I could buy that kind of shit! I can't even afford to send a package with a gift in it to Ben yet he's mailing me a plushie cause he knows how much I love Sonic and those characters. 

Surgery this summer...no flow of cash...Going home next weekend to see a play. I'm also seeing a play during winter and summer break. Should be fun. 

Taking 16 credits next semester. I'll post my schedule during winter break. 

Thats about all. 

Time to go back to work on Silence.

Meep. Dun like taking medicine and I hate going to the hospital and I hate, hate doctors. The reason? 
1) I hate doctors just because I do.
2) I hate hospitals cause they always keep you waiting! Like when I dislocated my jaw. I waited for 2 hours and 15 mins. 
3) I hate medicine cause it either makes you tired or it tastes really nasty! Really nasty!
